    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入我们的游戏讨论群</h2>官方玩家群：548253790<br>如加群时提示群已满，欢迎加入2群 ：996760787<br>我们期望听到你的声音!<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/8524ee1b7c6c92a4adc9f8e9375e5993.poster.avif?t=1769570961\" width=592 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/8524ee1b7c6c92a4adc9f8e9375e5993.webm?t=1769570961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/8524ee1b7c6c92a4adc9f8e9375e5993.mp4?t=1769570961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新感觉！骰型构筑Roguelite游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——在《骰号大厨》的世界里，六面骰上的点数由你自己决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集食材和厨具，分配给各位骰厨，就能定制每一面的点数。通过骰出的点数出餐，完成一个接一个愈发艰难的挑战，让你的厨艺登峰造极。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/ba4bbc592cc1a5c1bb7c30a0f4e729f8.avif?t=1769570961\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>展现厨艺，从严选食材开始</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食材的大小、形状、点数都不尽相同，需要通过摆放位置让骰厨们物尽其用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，食材的分配不仅关系到骰厨们的骰型，也决定了菜单上的菜品种类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此通过分配食材让骰厨们的骰型更容易达成菜单上菜品的要求，是经营厨房的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/ca3a6709611d3b44990d655f0b17335e.poster.avif?t=1769570961\" width=600 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/ca3a6709611d3b44990d655f0b17335e.webm?t=1769570961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357970/extras/ca3a6709611d3b44990d655f0b17335e.mp4?t=1769570961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组合菜品，让出餐事半功倍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和食材一样，各类菜品也是千差万别，有追求新鲜度的海鲜料理，也有考验火候的各种烤肉，还有为其他料理提供加成的各式配菜……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情探索菜品间的组合搭配，让简单的料理也能获得高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管控风险，让你的餐厅蒸蒸日上</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一味地追求高级菜品或许会让你的骰厨们不堪重负，如果不能如愿出餐你将承受巨大风险。而倘若过于谨小慎微，菜单上只保留简单好做的菜品，你也将很快面临入不敷出的窘境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但不用担心，即使失败了，下一局你也将从更高的起点出发！</strong></p>",
